Class NiryoOneModel

java.lang.Object
at.jku.swe.simcomp.azureadapter.service.NiryoOneModel.NiryoOneModel
public class NiryoOneModel extends Object
The NiryoOneModel class represents the joint angles of a Niryo One robotic arm.
